# Installation of GHC 8.0.0

## Installation Script

~~~
# get distribution   
cd $HOME/Downloads  
wget http://downloads.haskell.org/~ghc/8.0.1-rc4/ghc-8.0.0.20160421-x86_64-deb8-linux.tar.xz
 
tar xvfJ ghc-8.0.0.20160421-x86_64-deb8-linux.tar.xz
cd ghc-8.0.0.20160421 

# install  
mkdir $HOME/Software/ghc-8.0.0  

./configure --prefix=$HOME/Software/ghc-8.0.0  
make install

# cleanup: remove temporary files  
cd ..  
rm -rfv ghc-8.0.0*
~~~

## Activation Script

~~~
switchghc 8.0.0 
